This is highly improbable and likely an error, as JVLS's contribution is primarily cash and significantly smaller in the description. explanation: Several issues exist here. Firstly, the language describing BorrowMoney.com's duties is informal, incomplete, and unstructured (e.g., "HTML code, build..."). The asterisk is most likely indicating that wording has been removed. This shows structural flaws. Secondly, the term "medical dispatch personal & product service" is vague. Thirdly, JVLS, LLC's contribution description is problematic, stating "Plus (10%) Of Any Generated Gross Revenue From Awarded Contract, In Addition to The Total Contributions." This is a structural flaw, not properly conveying information.
